    ">\n<html><head><meta name=\"qrichtext\" content=\"1\" /><style type=\"text/css\">\np, li { white-space: pre-wrap; "
    "}\n</style></head><body align=\"left\" style=\" font-family:'Helvetica'; font-size:12px; font-weight:400; font-sty"
    "le:normal;\">\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -q"
    "t-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16px; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\""
    ">Inputs</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0p"
    "x; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16px; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underli"
    "ne;\">Outputs</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-ri"
    "ght:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12px; font-weight:600;\">reset_integrator"
    "</span><span style=\" font-size:12px;\">: Quando true, apaga o erro acumulado dos integradores.</span></p>\n<p ali"
    "gn=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; tex"
    "t-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12px; font-weight:600;\">enable_sm</span><span style=\" font-size:12px;\""
    ">: Quando true, habilita a alimentação do motor de passo (sem necessariamente movimentá-lo). Quando false, libera "
    "a direção.</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right"
    ":0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12px; font-weight:600;\">enable_control</spa"
    "n><span style=\" font-size:12px;\">: Quando true, habilita o controlador. Quando false, a entrada dos integradores"
    " e a saída de atuação são nulas.</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-"
    "left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:12px; font-weight:600;"
    "\">ready</span><span style=\" font-size:12px;\">: Flag que indica que o controlador está atuando, ou está pronto p"
    "ara atuar. True nos estados ON e WAIT.</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\"-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:"
    "0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><br /></p>\n<p a"
    "lign=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; t"
    "ext-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:16px; font-weight:600; text-decoration: underline;\">States</span></p>\n"
    "<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:"
    "0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\">CONTROL_OFF</span><span style=\" font-size"
    ":11px;\">:</span><span style=\" font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\"> E</span><span style=\" font-size:11px;\">stado"
    " inicial. Controlador desligado, integrador resetado e motor desligado.</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" mar"
    "gin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span st"
    "yle=\" font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\">CONTROL_INIT: </span><span style=\" font-size:11px;\">Motor é ligado. Pa"
    "ra chegar neste estado, é necessário um enable e que o veículo esteja andando ou parado (sem ré)</span></p>\n<p al"
    "ign=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; te"
    "xt-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\">CONTROL_WAIT: </span><span style=\" font-size:1"
    "1px;\">Controlador desligado e motor ligado. Só permanece neste estado se modo_veiculo=Parado e enable=true.</span"
    "></p>\n<p align=\"left\" style=\" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-"
    "indent:0; text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\" font-size:11px; font-weight:600;\">CONTROL_ON: </span><span style=\" f"
    "ont-size:11px;\">Controlador e motor ligados. Só permanece neste estado se modo_veiculo=Andando e enable=true.</sp"
    "an></p></body></html>"
